This is a discontinued original version of the very first of Nancy Drew series, Secrets Can Kill. THIS IS NOT REMASTERED VERSION!

How to install/run
1. Burn or mount ISO
2. When mounted/inserted, you gonna have to locate the CD-Rom drive's root folder and execute SETUP.exe manually because autorun.inf file is missing from the disk.
3. Skip DirectX setup unless you have a very OLD computer.
4. When asked to insert DISK 2 during the play, ALT-TAB will make it easier for you.

Enjoy the game.
